                                                                                <p>Paid on arrival, this applies to Haypole Barn and Sandmartins £100/cottage which will be returned within 7 days of departure pending checks.</p>

                                                                            </div>
                                                                        </div>
                                                                    </li>
                                                                    <li class="">
                                                                        <div class="grve-title"> Groceries and shopping </div>
                                                                        <div class="grve-content">
                                                                            <div class="grve-element grve-text">
                                                                                <p>
                                                                                    Launceston has some wonderful shops for fresh meat, fish, greengroceries and bakeries.
                                                                                    <br>

                                                                                    Supermarkets&nbsp; Asda, Waitrose and Tesco deliver from online orders.
                                                                                </p>

                                                                            </div>
                                                                        </div>
                                                                    </li>
                                                                    <li class="">
                                                                        <div class="grve-title"> Linen </div>
                                                                        <div class="grve-content">
                                                                            <div class="grve-element grve-text">
                                                                                <p>
                                                                                    All bed linen provided.
                                                                                    <br>

                                                                                    Both feather and hollowfill pillows available.
                                                                                    <br>

                                                                                    Tea towels provided, the number depends on size of cottage.
                                                                                    <br>

                                                                                    Oven gloves provided.
                                                                                </p>

                                                                            </div>
                                                                        </div>
                                                                    </li>
                                                                    <li class="">
                                                                        <div class="grve-title"> Bathroom Towels </div>
                                                                        <div class="grve-content">
                                                                            <div class="grve-element grve-text">
                                                                                <p>
                                                                                    Optional bath sheet and hand towel set can be hired for £5/week.
                                                                                    <br>

                                                                                    Please do not take them to the beach or the swimming pool!
                                                                                    <br>

                                                                                    Extra disability equipment &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Shower chairs can be reserved at the time of booking for use in Kingfisher Cottage, Haypole Barn or Sandmartins.
                                                                                </p>

                                                                            </div>
                                                                        </div>
                                                                    </li>
                                                                    <li class="">
                                                                        <div class="grve-title"> In the Laundry room</div>
                                                                        <div class="grve-content">
                                                                            <div class="grve-element grve-text">
                                                                                <p>
                                                                                    There are washing machines and a tumble drier on a £1 meter.
                                                                                    <br>

                                                                                    A pay phone with freephone to doctor.
                                                                                    <br>

                                                                                    (NB. Mobile signal can be variable, for info, refer to your network coverage checker.)
                                                                                    <br>

                                                                                    A deep freeze full of Callestick Icecream&nbsp; and lollies. Payment&nbsp; into an honesty box.
                                                                                </p>

                                                                            </div>
                                                                        </div>
                                                                    </li>
                                                                    <li class="">
                                                                        <div class="grve-title"> For babies</div>
                                                                        <div class="grve-content">
                                                                            <div class="grve-element grve-text">
                                                                                <p>
                                                                                    One travel cot and high chair in each cottage, if more are required, please ask.
                                                                                    <br>

                                                                                    No cot bedding is supplied.
                                                                                    <br>

                                                                                    All cottages with stairs have fitted stair gates top and bottom.
                                                                                    <br>

                                                                                    Baby cutlery and tableware in all cottages.
                                                                                </p>

                                                                            </div>
                                                                        </div>
                                                                    </li>
