                                                                        <div class="grve-content">
                                                                            <div class="grve-element grve-text">
                                                                                <p>All cottages have separate wifi as standard. No charge. WEP code secure.</p>

                                                                            </div>
                                                                        </div>
                                                                    </li>
                                                                    <li class="">
                                                                        <div class="grve-title"> Barbecues</div>
                                                                        <div class="grve-content">
                                                                            <div class="grve-element grve-text">
                                                                                <p>A selection of barbecues are available for your use, both gas and charcoal.</p>

                                                                            </div>
                                                                        </div>
                                                                    </li>
                                                                    <li class="">
                                                                        <div class="grve-title"> Information Folder</div>
                                                                        <div class="grve-content">
                                                                            <div class="grve-element grve-text">
                                                                                <p>
                                                                                    There will be a full inventory in the information folder in each cottage.
                                                                                    <br>

                                                                                    Also, information about our recycling regime, which we hope you will do your best with, even though you are on holiday!
                                                                                    <br>

                                                                                    Suggestions about places to go and things to do.
                                                                                    <br>

                                                                                    A list of emergency phone numbers.
                                                                                    <br>

                                                                                    The very important rules and regulations regarding use of the swimming pool.
                                                                                    <br>

                                                                                    Fire safety information.
                                                                                </p>

                                                                            </div>
                                                                        </div>
                                                                    </li>
