                                                                        <div class="grve-title"> Catering picture of food</div>
                                                                        <div class="grve-content">
                                                                            <div class="grve-element grve-text">
                                                                                <p>For those wanting to return to their cottage after a day out, to a no fuss, no preparation meal, then we can organise a local chef to make your meal and bring it to the cottage ready for you to pop in the oven.&nbsp; Please request details at time of booking.</p>

                                                                            </div>
                                                                        </div>
                                                                    </li>
                                                                    <li class="">
                                                                        <div class="grve-title"> Dogs</div>
                                                                        <div class="grve-content">
                                                                            <div class="grve-element grve-text">
                                                                                <p>One dog welcome in The Old Apple Tallet and in Swallow Barn in low season weeks. £20/week/dog.</p>

                                                                            </div>
