                                        <div class="grve-post-content">
                                            <p>Another large cottage with an airy and light open plan living area. French doors open out onto a private, sunny patio which is perfect for barbecuing and al fresco eating.</p>
                                            <p>There are 4 bedrooms in Sandmartins:</p>
                                            <p>Upstairs: Two pretty double rooms, both with en suite shower rooms plus a bunks room with another bathroom close by.</p>
                                            <p>Downstairs: A comfortable double bedroom with en suite wet room, also suitable for those with mobility problems.</p>
                                            <p>The kitchen has everything you will need for your holiday catering and includes a  range cooker, microwave plus all our standard fixtures and fittings.</p>
                                            <p>
                                                This cottage can be opened up on the ground floor to link through to 
                                                <a title="Haypole Barn" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20240723165628/http://www.waterloofarmholidays.co.uk/haypole-barn/">
                                                    <strong>Haypole Barn </strong>
                                                </a>
                                                next door, creating a 16 person holiday barn.
                                            </p>
